data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT** This captivating like new two story home is the perfect blend of comfort, style and functionality. Home has 5 spacious bedrooms and 4 full baths, nestled in a highly sought after neighborhood and school district.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an expansive open floor plan complemented by modern design and finishes. The main floor includes the one stand out feature, a gourmet kitchen which opens seamlessly into the keeping room which features one of the 2 fireplaces. It boast new gorgeous to the ceiling lighted cabinets, a large breakfast bar/island, upgraded counter tops with Calcutta Quartz. Also, on the main floor you will find one of five bedrooms with a full bath. Great for for overnight guest or ideal for multi-generational living. Journey upstairs to find 4 more bedrooms and 3 full baths, with newly upgraded carpet. You also find a spacious media room great for family entertainment. Along with a office nook or study. The oversized owners suit features a sitting area to enjoy  morning coffee or tea. Owners bath features his and hers separated vanities, soaking tub with separate shower and large walk in closet. All bedrooms are luxurious and well-appointed. This stunning newly painted (exterior and interior) home sits on a large corner lot facing the cut-de-sac. Along with the well landscaped fenced back yard, this space invites outdoor entertaining and provides a safe secure area, for family, pets and outdoor fun. Residing in this prestigious community you can enjoy the sparkling pool perfect for summer fun. Don't miss the opportunity to live in this like-new home, with so many stunning upgrades. Welcome Home!
